---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for MortgageDash."
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-24">
    <div class="card p-8 sm:p-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8" style="color: var(--text-primary);">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-6" style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
        <p>Last updated: June 19, 2026</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>MortgageDash is a client-side calculator. We do <strong>not</strong> collect, store, or transmit any of the personal financial data you enter into our calculators (e.g., home price, income, down payment). All calculations are performed locally in your web browser.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>Because we do not collect your financial data, we do not use it for any purpose. We may use anonymous, aggregated analytics (such as page views or state calculator usage) to improve our website's performance and user experience.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">3. Cookies and Advertising</h2>
        <p>We use local storage strictly to remember your UI preferences, such as your choice between Dark Mode and Light Mode. Additionally, this website partners with Google AdSense to serve advertisements when you visit our pages.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads on MortgageDash. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to our users based on their visit to this site and/or other sites on the Internet. Users may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://myadcenter.google.com/" target="_blank" class="text-[#06b6d4] hover:underline" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ad Settings</a> or <a href="https://aboutads.info" target="_blank" class="text-[#06b6d4] hover:underline" rel="noopener noreferrer">aboutads.info</a>.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">4. Third-Party Links and Services</h2>
        <p>Our website contains links to external web assets and state tax resources. We do not control or hold liability for the privacy practices of these third parties. Please note that third-party ad vendors and ad networks may also serve cookies on our site to measure ad effectiveness. You can choose to disable or selectively turn off our cookies or third-party cookies in your browser settings.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-[#06b6d4] hover:underline">Contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
